,{"pid":"cc1f76c366226cb6c9f36c5ade46bf5f87a0d3ce","tid":1556431,"uid":263219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a0979922258362d4ccaecd643b2147fd0953e8b","tid":1556431,"uid":34144,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T19:27:44.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">羅范慰蛆<br />\n己亥年夏羅門范氏慰蛆記</div><br />\n<br />\n己亥年夏，酷吏欲行送中惡法，民不畏威，五月初七，流水起義，歷時三月，氣勢若虹。<br />\n<br />\n苛政鄙陋，衙役厭民所生，狎民所居，以死懼民。或重杖加身，或狼煙燻襲，或火器誅首，無所不用其極，欲教蒼生盡成寒蟬。惡役狀若瘋魔，恃勢橫行，下欺婦孺，上辱通判，時人無不唾曰糞蛆。<br />\n<br />\n昔有營妓羅門范氏，貌極寢，尤好吞吐糞蛆之道，蛆甚好之，乃至一夜連御七十蛆，奢淫無道，風化盡喪。<br />\n<br />\n八月十一，東窗事發，羅范大驚，遂造空穴之謠，誣民作妓，以莫須有罪之。民不恥，詰曰 : 「羅范者，慰蛆營妓也。」寡廉鮮恥，賊喊捉賊，謂之曰羅范慰蛆。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:25:58.000Z","msg":"貌極寢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尤好吞吐糞蛆之道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d796898ad181ce7dd7f364bd7f9a2c553dfacd","tid":1556431,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3c1d787e8ff8ad2c085fcb27d793df7654daeb","tid":1556431,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34f542ae211a08e3b43069a80bec8dc196440c5","tid":1556431,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:05:40.000Z","msg":